9
00:00:59,254 --> 00:01:03,054
Changing, soaring

10
00:01:03,054 --> 00:01:06,854
Even if the sky is distant

11
00:01:08,264 --> 00:01:12,034
I want to tell you that this passion

12
00:01:12,034 --> 00:01:15,594
Gives me the strength to never give in

13
00:01:15,674 --> 00:01:19,274
I won't hesitate anymore

14
00:01:19,274 --> 00:01:24,944
I'm starting up so I can be myself

15
00:02:03,924 --> 00:02:08,154
Bokutou Police Station's Best Partners


16
00:02:08,154 --> 00:02:08,624
Bokutou Police Station


17
