Bokutou Police Station
I'm very sorry!

18
00:02:10,624 --> 00:02:13,524
Officer Saga's injuries were entirely my fault!


19
00:02:13,864 --> 00:02:16,884
I was inattentive while on duty.

20
00:02:17,264 --> 00:02:21,134
I take complete responsibility and
will accept any punishment.

21
00:02:21,404 --> 00:02:23,034
Hold on, Tsujimoto.

22
00:02:23,034 --> 00:02:26,704
It wasn't all that big of an accident,
so there's no need to...

23
00:02:26,704 --> 00:02:28,574
But when it occurred, I was...

24
00:02:28,574 --> 00:02:29,904
Good morning!

25
00:02:30,484 --> 00:02:31,584
Saori!

26
00:02:31,584 --> 00:02:33,454
You're well enough to return already?

27
00:02:33,454 --> 00:02:35,154
I'm sorry for all the trouble!

28
00:02:35,154 --> 00:02:37,654
Hey, are you sure you should be here?

29
00:02:37,654 --> 00:02:39,784
Yes! It's only a sprain!

30
00:02:39,784 --> 00:02:42,654
See? I'm fine!

31
00:02:43,924 --> 00:02:44,724
Saori!

32
