Saori!
Saori!

33
00:02:44,794 --> 00:02:45,594
Saori!

34
00:02:45,594 --> 00:02:47,084
Don't push yourself!

35
00:02:48,534 --> 00:02:52,834
Sorry, Senpai. I should've been more attentive.


36
00:02:53,604 --> 00:02:55,374
Saori! Saori!

37
00:02:55,374 --> 00:02:57,234
Are you all right, Saori?

38
00:02:58,074 --> 00:02:59,104
Saori!

39
00:02:59,104 --> 00:03:00,174
I'm okay.

40
00:03:00,174 --> 00:03:02,164
Ow!

41
00:03:04,414 --> 00:03:05,844
Natsumi Senpai...

42
00:03:06,244 --> 00:03:09,514
Everyone... I'm sorry for all the trouble I caused.

43
00:03:09,514 --> 00:03:10,454
You don't need to apologize...

44
00:03:10,454 --> 00:03:15,324
But the greatest fault lies with the dangerous
drivers who drive on streets closed to traffic!

45
00:03:15,324 --> 00:03:21,294
Cracking down on them is our job
as police officers,

46
00:03:21,294 --> 00:03:25,734
and it is my duty to keep public order
and maintain peace!

47
00:03:25,734 --> 00:03:29,934
I can't take time off just because of a sprain.
Right, Senpai?

48
00:03:29,934 --> 00:03:30,844
Huh?

49
00:03:30,844 --> 00:03:32,674
Officer Saga is right!

50
00:03:32,674 --> 00:03:34,974
Don't you agree, Tsujimoto?

51
00:03:34,974 --> 00:03:36,774
Look after her until the end.

52
00:03:36,774 --> 00:03:40,214
It's not like you to leave a job undone...

53
00:03:40,214 --> 00:03:41,414
Undone?

54
00:03:41,414 --> 00:03:42,614
Natsumi Senpai!

55
00:03:42,614 --> 00:03:45,784
Please train me fully! I'm counting on you!


56
00:03:46,554 --> 00:03:47,754
Saori...

57
00:03:51,124 --> 00:03:52,494
All right, then!

58
00:03:53,694 --> 00:03:55,994
Everyone, sorry for all the trouble I caused!

59
00:03:55,994 --> 00:03:57,564
You're right!

60
00:03:57,564 --> 00:04:00,004
I should give it my best shot, like I always do!

61
00:04:00,504 --> 00:04:04,444
I'll start by totally getting rid of
those nasty shortcut drivers!

62
00:04:04,444 --> 00:04:07,274
Everyone! We'll need your help!

63
00:04:07,274 --> 00:04:10,244
All right!

64
00:04:10,244 --> 00:04:13,414
Why don't we print leaflets telling people
not to use the shortcuts?

65
00:04:13,414 --> 00:04:15,184
That's a great idea.

66
00:04:15,184 --> 00:04:16,984
I'll do my best, too!

67
00:04:16,984 --> 00:04:19,424
I'm really sorry about your leg.

68
00:04:19,424 --> 00:04:20,524
Saga!

69
00:04:20,524 --> 00:04:21,524
Yes, sir!

70
00:04:21,524 --> 00:04:25,064
I understand how you feel, but I'm assigning
you desk work for the time being.

71
00:04:25,064 --> 00:04:28,364
You can't do that! I really am fit for duty.

72
00:04:28,364 --> 00:04:29,624
I'm sorry.

73
00:04:30,264 --> 00:04:33,304
Leave it to me! I'll cover your share, as well!

74
00:04:33,304 --> 00:04:34,574
I'm so sorry...

75
00:04:34,574 --> 00:04:37,234
I'm of no use when you need me most.

76
00:04:37,544 --> 00:04:40,664
Forget it! I'm the one at fault.

77
00:04:41,744 --> 00:04:45,284
She's right! Natsumi has no problem
working for two!

78
00:04:45,284 --> 00:04:46,514
It'll be a breeze.

79
00:04:46,514 --> 00:04:48,314
Should I have said "eating for two"?

80
00:04:48,314 --> 00:04:49,714
Yoriko!

81
00:04:49,714 --> 00:04:50,844
Chief.

82
00:04:51,454 --> 00:04:54,754
Let us use the patrol routes from my simulation.

83
00:04:54,754 --> 00:04:56,154
Yes, of course.

84
00:04:56,154 --> 00:04:57,394
What is that?

85
00:04:57,394 --> 00:05:00,864
I used the maps from the shortcut guide

86
00:05:00,864 --> 00:05:04,104
to create a simulation that will enable us
to patrol them efficiently.

87
00:05:04,104 --> 00:05:06,104
I hope it will help everyone.

88
00:05:06,104 --> 00:05:08,964
Way to go, Miyuki! We can always count on you!

89
00:05:09,304 --> 00:05:11,704
All right, everyone to the conference room.

90
00:05:11,704 --> 00:05:12,544
Yes, sir!

91
00:05:12,544 --> 00:05:16,114
These red marks indicate shortcut checkpoints.

92
00:05:16,114 --> 00:05:21,254
I compiled patrol routes that correspond
to times when traffic is heaviest.

93
00:05:21,254 --> 00:05:25,984
There are three routes, and four checkpoints
that change every four hours.

94
00:05:25,984 --> 00:05:29,694
Since these will be done
in addition to regular patrols,

95
00:05:29,694 --> 00:05:32,764
we'll need the cooperation of everyone
in our Traffic Section.

96
