Bokutou Station and being paired with you...

355
00:18:35,374 --> 00:18:37,614
It all seems like only yesterday.

356
00:18:37,614 --> 00:18:41,204
But time continuously moves on.

357
00:18:41,614 --> 00:18:46,754
