but some people think it makes the ride too soft.

375
00:19:50,714 --> 00:19:52,054
What do you think?

376
00:19:52,054 --> 00:19:57,824
I'm finding that assumptions
from my car days don't apply.

377
00:19:57,824 --> 00:20:02,164
